{
    "name": "Wild Lancer",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Tactics",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>During Combat</b> The barbarian makes charge attacks whenever possible. If prevented from charging, she maneuvers to maximize attacks of opportunity caused by her extended reach. Her armor spikes are a weapon of last resort.<br/><b>Base Statistics </b>When not raging, the barbarian\u2019s statistics are <b>AC </b>20, touch 11, flat-footed 19; <b>hp </b>53; <b>Fort </b>+7, <b>Will </b>+3; no bonus vs. spells and spell-like or supernatural abilities; <b>Melee </b>mwk lance +10 (1d8+4/\u00d73) or armor spikes +9 (1d6+4); <b>Ranged </b>javelin +6 (1d6+4); <b>Str </b>18, <b>Con </b>14; <b>CMB </b>+9; <b>Skills </b>Climb +10, Swim +5."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "Some barbarians are most at home on horseback."
        }
    ],
